Name: OverlapMultiByObjectType
Description: Test the collision of a shape at the supplied location using object types, and determine the set of components that it overlaps

Name: SpawnActorDeferred
Description: Allowing you to modify properties or set up the actor before it's fully initialized and added to the level

Name: GetDeltaSeconds
Description: Returns the frame delta time in seconds adjusted by e.g. time dilation

Name: GetFirstLocalPlayerFromController
Description: Get the first valid local player via the first player controller

Name: ServerTravel
Description: The  function is used in Unreal Engine to initiate a server-side map travel. This means that the server will load the specified map, and all connected clients will follow the server to the new map.
